      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * TRATTAMENTO TOTALI DOCUMENTO E TESTATA DI PRIMANOTA(IVA)  *
      *    *===========================================================*
      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Routine pre-trattamento testata registrazione 2           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pre-te2-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su impostazione righe del documento        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-cod-tmf-ird    =    "N"
                     go to pre-te2-reg-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione totali riga                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-tot-rig-000      thru det-tot-rig-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione codici iva per testata 2     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-civ-te2-000      thru det-civ-te2-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione totali riepilogo documento   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-tri-doc-000      thru det-tri-doc-999        .
       pre-te2-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Determinazione numero pagine che compongono la testata 2  *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       dmp-te2-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * La testata 2 e' composta di nr. 2 pagine        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      2                    to   w-cnt-sts-imp-mt2      .
       dmp-te2-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Determinazione si/no pagina w-cnt-sts-imp-np2 da trattare *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       snp-te2-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione flag di uscita                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-sts-imp-snp      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione in funzione del numero pagina        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     snp-te2-reg-100
                     snp-te2-reg-200
                     depending            on   w-cnt-sts-imp-np2      .
           go to     snp-te2-reg-999.
       snp-te2-reg-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pagina 1 : accettata solo se impostazione righe *
      *              *            del documento                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-cod-tmf-ird    =    "N"
                     move  "#"            to   w-cnt-sts-imp-snp      .
           go to     snp-te2-reg-999.
       snp-te2-reg-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pagina 2 : accettata solo se registrazione con- *
      *              *            tabile da eseguire                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-cod-tmf-ccg    =    zero
                     move  "#"            to   w-cnt-sts-imp-snp      .
           go to     snp-te2-reg-999.
       snp-te2-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione testata 2 registrazione                      *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-te2-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Status impostazione                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-sts-imp-te2      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione tipo uscita                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione function-key                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   v-key                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo impostazione : testata                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "T"                  to   w-cnt-mfu-tip-imp      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazioni                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Deviazione in funzione del numero pagina    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-te2-reg-100
                     acc-te2-reg-200
                     depending            on   w-cnt-sts-imp-np2      .
           go to     acc-te2-reg-999.
       acc-te2-reg-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Totale sconto in chiusura                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-tot-scc-000      thru acc-tot-scc-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
       acc-te2-reg-110.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice iva sconto in chiusura               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-civ-scc-000      thru acc-civ-scc-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-te2-reg-100.
       acc-te2-reg-120.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Totale sconto pagamento                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-tot-scp-000      thru acc-tot-scp-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-te2-reg-110.
           if        v-key                =    "DOWN"
                     go to acc-te2-reg-135.
       acc-te2-reg-130.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice iva sconto pagamento                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-civ-scp-000      thru acc-civ-scp-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-te2-reg-120.
       acc-te2-reg-135.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Inizializzazione contatore per tabella spese*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      1                    to   w-acc-iep-spe-ctr      .
       acc-te2-reg-140.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Si/No addebito, importo e percentuale spesa *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
       acc-te2-reg-142.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Accettazione Si/No addebito             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-spe-snx-000      thru acc-spe-snx-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se Up                                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                not  = "UP  "
                     go to acc-te2-reg-144.
           subtract  1                    from w-acc-iep-spe-ctr      .
           if        w-acc-iep-spe-ctr    =    zero
                     go to acc-te2-reg-130
           else      go to acc-te2-reg-142.
       acc-te2-reg-144.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se Down                                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DOWN"
                     go to acc-te2-reg-148.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Accettazione importo spesa              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-spe-imp-000      thru acc-spe-imp-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-te2-reg-142.
       acc-te2-reg-146.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Accettazione codice iva spesa           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-spe-civ-000      thru acc-spe-civ-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-te2-reg-144.
       acc-te2-reg-148.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se Down o Return                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-acc-iep-spe-ctr      .
           if        w-acc-iep-spe-ctr    >    w-prs-spe-fat-nst
                     go to acc-te2-reg-149
           else      go to acc-te2-reg-142.
       acc-te2-reg-149.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Inizializzazione contatore per tabella spese*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-prs-spe-fat-nst    to   w-acc-iep-spe-ctr      .
       acc-te2-reg-150.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Totale spese incasso                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-tot-spi-000      thru acc-tot-spi-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-te2-reg-140.
       acc-te2-reg-160.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice iva spese incasso                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-civ-spi-000      thru acc-civ-spi-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-te2-reg-150.
       acc-te2-reg-170.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Totale spese bollo                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-tot-spb-000      thru acc-tot-spb-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-te2-reg-160.
       acc-te2-reg-180.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice iva spese bollo                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-civ-spb-000      thru acc-civ-spb-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-te2-reg-170.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Next Screen                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "NXSC"
                     go to acc-te2-reg-190.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Presa visione per pagina testata 2          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-prv-pt2-000      thru acc-prv-pt2-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "NXSC"
                     move  "+"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-te2-reg-180.
       acc-te2-reg-190.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Caricamento castelletto Iva                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   car-cst-iva-000      thru car-cst-iva-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Flag di accettazione pagina testata 2 nr. 1 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-te2-fda-pt1 (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Fine Pagina                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "+"                  to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           go to     acc-te2-reg-999.
       acc-te2-reg-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Descrizione causale contabile               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-des-cau-000      thru acc-des-cau-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
       acc-te2-reg-205.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Data registrazione contabile                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-dat-mgd-000      thru acc-dat-mgd-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-te2-reg-200.
       acc-te2-reg-210.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Numero giornale iva                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-ngi-iva-000      thru acc-ngi-iva-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-te2-reg-205.
       acc-te2-reg-212.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Regime fiscale                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-flg-rfp-000      thru acc-flg-rfp-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-tes      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-te2-reg-210.
       acc-te2-reg-215.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Numero protocollo iva                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-npt-iva-000      thru acc-npt-iva-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-te2-reg-212.
       acc-te2-reg-220.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Castelletto iva                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-cst-iva-000      thru acc-cst-iva-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-te2-reg-215.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Next Screen                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "NXSC"
                     go to acc-te2-reg-290.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Presa visione per pagina testata 2          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-prv-pt2-000      thru acc-prv-pt2-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "NXSC"
                     move  "+"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-te2    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-te2-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-te2-reg-220.
       acc-te2-reg-290.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Flag di accettazione pagina testata 2 nr. 2 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-te2-fda-pt2 (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Fine Pagina                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "+"                  to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2      .
           go to     acc-te2-reg-999.
       acc-te2-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione testata registrazione 2                   *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-te2-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione in funzione del numero pagina        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-te2-reg-100
                     vis-te2-reg-200
                     depending            on   w-cnt-sts-imp-np2      .
           go to     vis-te2-reg-999.
       vis-te2-reg-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pagina 1                                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Totale sconto in chiusura                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-tot-scc-000      thru vis-tot-scc-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice iva sconto in chiusura               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-civ-scc-000      thru vis-civ-scc-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Totale sconto pagamento                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-tot-scp-000      thru vis-tot-scp-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice iva sconto pagamento                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-civ-scp-000      thru vis-civ-scp-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Si/No addebito spese                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-spe-snx-000      thru vis-spe-snx-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Importi spese                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-spe-imp-000      thru vis-spe-imp-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice iva spese                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-spe-civ-000      thru vis-spe-civ-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Totale spese incasso                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-tot-spi-000      thru vis-tot-spi-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice iva spese incasso                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-civ-spi-000      thru vis-civ-spi-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Totale spese bollo                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-tot-spb-000      thru vis-tot-spb-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice iva spese bollo                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-civ-spb-000      thru vis-civ-spb-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riepilogo totali                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-rie-tot-000      thru vis-rie-tot-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Fine Pagina                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-te2-reg-999.
       vis-te2-reg-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pagina 2                                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Descrizione causale contabile               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-des-cau-000      thru vis-des-cau-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Data registrazione contabile                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-dat-mgd-000      thru vis-dat-mgd-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Numero giornale iva                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-ngi-iva-000      thru vis-ngi-iva-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Regime fiscale                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-flg-rfp-000      thru vis-flg-rfp-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Numero protocollo iva                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-npt-iva-000      thru vis-npt-iva-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Castelletto iva                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cst-iva-000      thru vis-cst-iva-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Fine Pagina                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-te2-reg-999.
       vis-te2-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompts testata 2                         *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-te2-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Erase linee impegnate dalla testata 2           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "EL"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      21                   to   v-lto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione in funzione del numero pagina        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-te2-reg-100
                     pmt-te2-reg-200
                     depending            on   w-cnt-sts-imp-np2      .
           go to     pmt-te2-reg-999.
       pmt-te2-reg-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pagina 1                                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Intestazione pagina totali                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Fincatura                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "          Voce                   Importo    Iva   
      -              "|            Totali           "
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sottolineatura fincatura                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "------------------------- ---------------- -----  
      -              "| ----------------------------"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Trattini verticali                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      5                    to   w-pmt-te2-reg-ctr      .
       pmt-te2-reg-110.
           add       1                    to   w-pmt-te2-reg-ctr      .
           if        w-pmt-te2-reg-ctr    >    21
                     go to pmt-te2-reg-120.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      01                   to   v-car                  .
           move      w-pmt-te2-reg-ctr    to   v-lin                  .
           move      51                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "|"                  to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           go to     pmt-te2-reg-110.
       pmt-te2-reg-120.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Sconto in chiusura                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-tot-scc-000      thru pmt-tot-scc-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Sconto pagamento                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-tot-scp-000      thru pmt-tot-scp-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Importi spese                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-spe-imp-000      thru pmt-spe-imp-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Spese incasso                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-tot-spi-000      thru pmt-tot-spi-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Spese bollo                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-tot-spb-000      thru pmt-tot-spb-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riepilogo totali                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-rie-tot-000      thru pmt-rie-tot-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Fine Pagina                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-te2-reg-999.
       pmt-te2-reg-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pagina 2                                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Descrizione causale contabile               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-des-cau-000      thru pmt-des-cau-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Data registrazione contabile                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-dat-mgd-000      thru pmt-dat-mgd-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Numero giornale iva                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-ngi-iva-000      thru pmt-ngi-iva-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Regime fiscale                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-flg-rfp-000      thru pmt-flg-rfp-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Numero protocollo iva                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-npt-iva-000      thru pmt-npt-iva-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Trattini a linea 09                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      09                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      all "-"              to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Castelletto iva                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-cst-iva-000      thru pmt-cst-iva-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Fine Pagina                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-te2-reg-999.
       pmt-te2-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompts per sconto in chiusura            *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-tot-scc-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      26                   to   v-car                  .
           move      07                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Sconto incondizionato    :"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       pmt-tot-scc-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompts per sconto pagamento              *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-tot-scp-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      26                   to   v-car                  .
           move      08                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Sconto pagamento         :"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       pmt-tot-scp-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompts per importi spese                 *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-spe-imp-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se nessuna personalizzazione : uscita           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-spe-fat-nst    =    zero
                     go to pmt-spe-imp-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ciclo di scansione su tabella spese             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-pmt-iep-spe-ctr      .
       pmt-spe-imp-100.
           add       1                    to   w-pmt-iep-spe-ctr      .
           if        w-pmt-iep-spe-ctr    >    w-prs-spe-fat-nst
                     go to pmt-spe-imp-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      25                   to   v-car                  .
           add       09
                     w-pmt-iep-spe-ctr  giving v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-prs-spe-fat-dve
                    (w-pmt-iep-spe-ctr)   to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      01                   to   v-car                  .
           add       09
                     w-pmt-iep-spe-ctr  giving v-lin                  .
           move      26                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      ":"                  to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-spe-imp-100.
       pmt-spe-imp-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompts per spese incasso                 *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-tot-spi-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      26                   to   v-car                  .
           move      19                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Spese incasso            :"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       pmt-tot-spi-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompts per spese bollo                   *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-tot-spb-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      26                   to   v-car                  .
           move      20                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Spese bollo              :"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       pmt-tot-spb-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompts per riepilogo totali              *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-rie-tot-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      12                   to   v-car                  .
           move      07                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      53                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Lordo      :"       to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      12                   to   v-car                  .
           move      09                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      53                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Netto      :"       to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      12                   to   v-car                  .
           move      11                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      53                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Spese      :"       to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      12                   to   v-car                  .
           move      13                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      53                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Imponibile :"       to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      12                   to   v-car                  .
           move      15                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      53                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Iva        :"       to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione a seconda che sia un documento in    *
      *              * valuta o no                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    =    c-sgl
                     go to pmt-rie-tot-100
           else      go to pmt-rie-tot-200.
       pmt-rie-tot-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se documento non in valuta                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      12                   to   v-car                  .
           move      18                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      53                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Totale     :"       to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           go to     pmt-rie-tot-999.
       pmt-rie-tot-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se documento in valuta                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Totale in valuta                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      12                   to   v-car                  .
           move      18                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      53                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-alf                  .
           string    "Totale "  delimited by   size
                     w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)
                                delimited by   size
                     " :"       delimited by   size
                                          into v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Totale in valuta base                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      12                   to   v-car                  .
           move      20                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      53                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-alf                  .
           string    "       "  delimited by   size
                     c-sgl      delimited by   size
                     " :"       delimited by   size
                                          into v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           go to     pmt-rie-tot-999.
       pmt-rie-tot-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompt : Descrizione causale contabile    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-des-cau-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      28                   to   v-car                  .
           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Causale contabile          :"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       pmt-des-cau-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompt : Data registrazione contabile     *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-dat-mgd-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      28                   to   v-car                  .
           move      07                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Data per la contabilita'   :"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       pmt-dat-mgd-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Prompt per : Numero giornale iva                          *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-ngi-iva-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se da visualizzare                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-cod-tmf-tpv    =    03
                     go to pmt-ngi-iva-999.
           if        w-prs-mul-gia-snx    not  = "S"
                     go to pmt-ngi-iva-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      20                   to   v-car                  .
           move      07                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      52                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Nr. giornale iva   :"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       pmt-ngi-iva-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Prompt per : Regime fiscale                               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-flg-rfp-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se da visualizzare                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-cod-tmf-tpv    not  = 01
                     go to pmt-flg-rfp-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      28                   to   v-car                  .
           move      08                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Regime fiscale             :"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       pmt-flg-rfp-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Prompt per campo : Numero protocollo iva                  *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-npt-iva-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se da visualizzare                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-cod-tmf-tpv    =    03
                     go to pmt-npt-iva-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      20                   to   v-car                  .
           move      08                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      52                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Protocollo iva     :"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       pmt-npt-iva-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Prompt per campo : Castelletto iva                        *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-cst-iva-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se da visualizzare                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-cod-tmf-tpv    =    03
                     go to pmt-cst-iva-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Deviazione a seconda che la sigla valuta    *
      *                  * sia o meno pari a quella base               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    =    c-sgl
                     go to pmt-cst-iva-100
           else      go to pmt-cst-iva-200.
       pmt-cst-iva-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se sigla valuta pari a quella base          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Fincatura                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      11                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "                   Codice iva     Imponibile      
      -              "   Imposta          Totale    "
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sottolineatura fincatura                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      12                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "                   ----------   --------------   -
      -              "-------------   --------------"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Trattini per totale                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      19                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "                               -------------------
      -              "------------------------------"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Literal per totali                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      08                   to   v-car                  .
           move      20                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      22                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Totali :"           to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Uscita                                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-cst-iva-999.
       pmt-cst-iva-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se sigla valuta diversa da quella base      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Fincatura                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      11                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Codice iva      In valuta         Imponibile      
      -              "   Imposta          Totale    "
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sottolineatura fincatura                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      12                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "----------   ---------------    --------------   -
      -              "-------------   --------------"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Trattini per totali                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      19                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "            --------------------------------------
      -              "------------------------------"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Literal per totali                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      08                   to   v-car                  .
           move      20                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      03                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Totali :"           to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Uscita                                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-cst-iva-999.
       pmt-cst-iva-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione campo testata 2 : Presa visione per pagina   *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-prv-pt2-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se non esiste alcuna pagina attiva successiva   *
      *              * alla pagina attuale : uscita                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Salvataggio numero pagina attuale           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-sts-imp-np2    to   w-cnt-sts-imp-svp      .
       acc-prv-pt2-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se all'ultima pagina : ripristino pagina    *
      *                  * salvata ed uscita                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-sts-imp-np2    not  < w-cnt-sts-imp-mt2
                     move  w-cnt-sts-imp-svp
                                          to   w-cnt-sts-imp-np2
                     go to acc-prv-pt2-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Incremento numero pagina                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-sts-imp-np2      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se pagina da trattare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   snp-te2-reg-000      thru snp-te2-reg-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se no : a re-incremento                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-sts-imp-snp    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-prv-pt2-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se si : ripristino pagina salvata e accet-  *
      *                  * tazione presa visione                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-sts-imp-svp    to   w-cnt-sts-imp-np2      .
       acc-prv-pt2-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione valore                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "MX"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "U"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      01                   to   v-car                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-msk                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-alf                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-not                  .
           move      "UP  "               to   v-pfk (01)             .
           move      "DOWN"               to   v-pfk (02)             .
           if        w-cnt-sts-imp-tes    not  = spaces and
                     w-cnt-sts-imp-cor    not  = spaces and
                     w-cnt-sts-imp-te2    not  = spaces and
                     w-cnt-sts-imp-co2    not  = spaces and
                     w-cnt-sts-imp-co3    not  = spaces and
                     w-cnt-sts-imp-pie    not  = spaces
                     move  "DO  "         to   v-pfk (05)             .
           move      "PRSC"               to   v-pfk (07)             .
           move      "NXSC"               to   v-pfk (08)             .
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-000      thru exe-acc-cmp-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Exit                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     move  "E"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2
                     go to acc-prv-pt2-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Delt                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DELT"
                     move  "X"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2
                     go to acc-prv-pt2-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Do                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     perform cnt-tdo-nok-000
                                          thru cnt-tdo-nok-999
                     if      w-cnt-tdo-nok-flg
                                          =    spaces
                             move  "S"    to   w-cnt-tus-acc-te2
                             go to acc-prv-pt2-999
                     else    move  spaces to   w-cnt-tdo-nok-flg
                             go to acc-prv-pt2-000.
       acc-prv-pt2-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione campo testata 2 : Totale sconto incondizio-  *
      *    * nato                                                      *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-tot-scc-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pre-accettazione                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Salvataggio valore precedente               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-te2-tot-scc (1)    to   w-sav-tot-scc          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Nxsc da campi della pagina precedenti    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
